OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat a leak-hit hospital after officials
OL,8,Fdiscovered parts of the roof have
OL,9,Frotted away.
OL,11,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,12,FBoard said a survey has identified
OL,13,F"more serious internal long-term
OL,14,Fdamage" to the roof of the Princess of
OL,15,FWales Hospital's main building in
OL,16,FBridgend, which will cost millions of
OL,17,Fpounds to repair.
