OL,6,FThe full statement from the health
OL,7,Fboard had said: "Following ongoing
OL,8,Fissues at Princess of Wales Hospital
OL,9,Fwith rain water entering the building
OL,10,Fthrough the roof, specialist
OL,11,Fcontractors have conducted a full
OL,12,Fsurvey of the condition of the roof of
OL,13,Fthe main building across the site.
OL,15,F"As well as informing some immediate
OL,16,Factions, that survey has identified
OL,17,Fmore serious internal long-term damage
OL,18,Fto the roof of the hospital that will
OL,19,Frequire an extensive programme of
OL,20,Freplacement and repair.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
