OL,6,F"We are dealing with this as a
OL,7,Fcritical incident, and are now
OL,8,Fexploring all options to ensure we can
OL,9,Fcontinue to provide care in a safe
OL,10,Fenvironment for those patients and
OL,11,Fstaff in our wards and those who will
OL,12,Fneed care in the future.
OL,14,F"The options will need to include the
