OL,7,Fbuildings in Wales "are reaching a
OL,8,Flife expectancy and things need
OL,9,Freplacing and repairing".
OL,11,FHe said: "We're doing that against the
OL,12,Fbackdrop of resources that are quite
OL,13,Fconstrained but I would also say that
OL,14,Fwe've been able to invest and put
OL,15,Fmoney into the things that are really
OL,16,Fimportant and clearly, as I said
